{"tid":1631961,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"作為一個和理非 我想感謝今日嘅勇武","createTime":"2019-10-06T16:41:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T17:11:36.000Z","uid":113865,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9102e98aae87165c28a3961f0c3d4d03801d2244","tid":1631961,"uid":113865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:41:15.000Z","msg":"好認同隔離post叫大家唔好上連登住 所以出埋呢個post就訓<br />\n<br />\n好想對今日出左黎嘅勇武手足講句多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無論今日嘅行動有幾多要檢討嘅地方都好 勇武手足嘅付出都係無庸置疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔想手足辛苦完返到屋企一上連登淨係睇到d屌勇武嘅post 真心會好灰好無力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n多謝各位勇武嘅付出 <br />\n無論點都好 我地都係坐埋同一條船 核爆都唔割！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49464a477062af4314750d6590b63dc31ee01869","tid":1631961,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:42:07.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n【重開】［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630849</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"eaf7eb0f48726bb18a7ad94d38e4ae717b0ab11f","tid":1631961,"uid":113865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:42:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"787142e006164debdb1e7ef37dd9e20dfe118b28","tid":1631961,"uid":113865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:42:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2a0d35423c8db22a6fbcd9724ea5fcb3d7bf5261","tid":1631961,"uid":105905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:42:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4ca56d10dd8ae23a94c67f945f292eb8e4467e9","tid":1631961,"uid":113865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:43:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e1095f158696e8da9c41ca6cbb5f6a011679dd87","tid":1631961,"uid":113865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:44:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5a613897196263d6d660ed2b7b5e4466e1810d09","tid":1631961,"uid":170808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9102e98aae87165c28a3961f0c3d4d03801d2244","tid":1631961,"uid":113865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:41:15.000Z","msg":"好認同隔離post叫大家唔好上連登住 所以出埋呢個post就訓<br />\n<br />\n好想對今日出左黎嘅勇武手足講句多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無論今日嘅行動有幾多要檢討嘅地方都好 勇武手足嘅付出都係無庸置疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔想手足辛苦完返到屋企一上連登淨係睇到d屌勇武嘅post 真心會好灰好無力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n多謝各位勇武嘅付出 <br />\n無論點都好 我地都係坐埋同一條船 核爆都唔割！！<img 